de.hft_stuttgart.storytellar

Class Trackable

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hft_stuttgart.storytellar.Trackable

  • public class Trackable
extends java.lang.Object
    Saves a trackable image. The trackable image is needed to define the position of a video/image on the screen. Trackable images were parsed from the XML and downloaded with the other media files.
    Author:
    Mirjam
